pageContext.claim: “And, by the way, I want China to do well, but they went down 32 percent over the last six months and we went way up. And since our election, we've gone up almost 50 percent.”
pageContext.analysis: The stock market has been increasing at an impressive rate, but it has gained closer to 25 percent than fifty percent. Plus the Chinese markets are down just over 25 percent for the year — not 32 percent in six months.
